Package io.github.ai4ci.output

Interface OutbreakFinalStateCSV

All Superinterfaces:
CommonCSV.Execution, CommonCSV.Model, CommonCSV.State, OutputWriter.Writeable
@Immutable public interface OutbreakFinalStateCSV extends CommonCSV.State
Final outbreak summary exported at simulation finish.

Main purpose: provide end-of-run aggregated metrics such as cumulative counts and maxima. Records are produced at the FINISH stage and are written once per simulation execution to a CSV file (final-state.csv).

Downstream uses: used for final result tables, calibration targets and quick comparison across simulation replications.

Author:
Rob Challen
